(94, 'Guinea-Bissau', 'GNB', 'gw.png', '<h1>Visa requirements for Bangladeshi citizens</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Visa_requirements_for_Bangladeshi_citizens#mw-head\">Jump to navigation</a><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Visa_requirements_for_Bangladeshi_citizens#searchInput\">Jump to search</a><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Bangladeshi_E_Passport.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e9/Bangladeshi_E_Passport.jpg/220px-Bangladeshi_E_Passport.jpg\" style=\"height:318px; width:220px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A (regular or ordinary)&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bangladeshi_passport\" title=\"Bangladeshi passport\">Bangladeshi passport</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Visa requirements for Bangladeshi citizens</strong>&nbsp;are administrative entry restrictions imposed on citizens of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bangladesh\" title=\"Bangladesh\">Bangladesh</a>&nbsp;by the authorities of other countries. As of 2&nbsp;July&nbsp;2019,&nbsp;Bangladeshi citizens who hold regular or ordinary Bangladeshi passports have visa free or visa on arrival access to 41 countries and territories, ranking the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bangladeshi_passport\" title=\"Bangladeshi passport\">Bangladeshi passport</a>&nbsp;101st in terms of travel freedom (tied with passports from Eritrea, Iran, Lebanon and North Korea) according to the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Henley_%26_Partners_Passport_Index\" title=\"Henley &amp; Partners Passport Index\">Henley Passport Index</a>.<sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Visa_requirements_for_Bangladeshi_citizens#cite_note-1\">[1]</a></sup>&nbsp;Bangladeshi citizens who hold Diplomatic passports and/or Official passports of Bangladesh have visa free or visa on arrival access to many more countries.<sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Visa_requirements_for_Bangladeshi_citizens#cite_note-2\">[2]</a></sup></p>\r\n\r\n<p><input type=\"checkbox\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Contents</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Visa_requirements_for_Bangladeshi_citizens#Visa_requirements_map\">1Visa requirements map</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Visa_requirements_for_Bangladeshi_citizens#Visa_requirements\">2Visa requirements</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Visa_requirements_for_Bangladeshi_citizens#Non-visa_restrictions\">3Non-visa restrictions</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Visa_requirements_for_Bangladeshi_citizens#See_also\">4See also</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Visa_requirements_for_Bangladeshi_citizens#References_and_Notes\">5References and Notes</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:22px\">for more information:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:22px\">&nbsp;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Visa_requirements_for_Bangladeshi_citizens</span></p>\r\n', '2018-09-11', '2021-02-18', 1),
