(109, 'Italy', 'ITA', 'it.png', '<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Information Visa Information:</strong><br />\r\nThe Embassy of Italy in Dhaka has appointed VFS Global as an outsourced partner, to facilitate applications for Italian visa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Italy Student Visa Processing Time:</strong><br />\r\nMinimum 21 Calendar Days required for applying study visa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;Visa Check List</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>This is a basic Italy student visa checklist. Required documents depending on student&rsquo;s profile. VISAThing for Student provides you complete visa application assistance.&nbsp;We provide information on Italy student visa agency in bd,Italy student visa agent, Italy student visa consultant, Italy job visa, Italy student visa ratio, Italy student visa documents,Italy student visa cost, Italy visa processing.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Need help, connect with our expert&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://visathingforstudent.com/inquiry/\">visa consultant</a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Passport:</strong>&nbsp;Passport must be valid for at least 3 months after planned departure date from Schengen area. The passport must have at least two blank and unmarked visa pages. If you want passport, please&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"http://www.passport.gov.bd/\">click here.</a></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Visa Application Form:</strong>&nbsp;A duly completed visa application form with date and signature</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Photo Specification:</strong>&nbsp;Recent 4.0 *3.5 cm size color photographs taken in last 6 months (white back ground only).</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Covering-Letter:</strong>&nbsp;Covering letter mentioning details of applicants, passport details, travel details and who will bear expenses details.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Confirmation of Enrolment:</strong>&nbsp;A &nbsp;Letter &nbsp;of &nbsp;Acceptance &nbsp;from &nbsp;the &nbsp;Irish &nbsp;university, college &nbsp;or &nbsp;school, confirming &nbsp;you have &nbsp;been &nbsp;accepted &nbsp;and &nbsp;enrolled &nbsp;on &nbsp;a course &nbsp;of &nbsp;full-time &nbsp;education.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Tuition Fees Payment Receipt:</strong>&nbsp;A payment receipt is a proof of payment that you have made payment to the institution.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Academic Documents:&nbsp;</strong>Please submit your all academic documents to Embassy/VAC</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Financials Means:</strong>&nbsp;Proof of financial means to cover the costs for the time of your studies.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Health Insurance:</strong>&nbsp;A proof of health insurance coverage whole period of study.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Birth Certificate:</strong>&nbsp;An original copy of Birth Registration Certificate. If you want Birth Registration Certificate please&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"http://bris.lgd.gov.bd/pub/application_form.aspx\">click here.</a></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Police Clearance:</strong>&nbsp;An original copy of Police Clearance Certificate. If you want Police Clearance Certificate please&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"http://pcc.police.gov.bd:8080/ords/f?p=500:1::::::\">click here.</a></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Accommodation Details:</strong>&nbsp;Once you have confirmed where you will be studying, you must need to show accommodation details.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px\">for more information :&nbsp;https://visathingforstudent.com/countries/italy/</span></p>\r\n', '2018-09-11', '2021-02-20', 1),
(110, 'Ivory Coast', 'CIV', 'ci.png', '<h1>Cote d&rsquo;Ivoire Visa from Bangladesh<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://visathing.com/continent/africa/\" rel=\"tag\">Africa</a></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Capital City:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abidjan</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Currency:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>CFA Franc (XOF)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Local Time:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GMT</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Telephone Code:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>+225</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bank:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Closed on Saturday and Sunday</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Exchange Rate:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.00 XOF (CFA Franc) is equivalent to 0.13 BDT</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>&nbsp;Basic information</h4>\r\n\r\n<h5>For&nbsp;Cote d&rsquo;Ivoire , VISAThing provides</h5>\r\n\r\n<h5><a href=\"https://visathing.com/visa-processing-logistics-support/\"><strong>&nbsp;Logistics support</strong></a></h5>\r\n\r\n<h5><a href=\"https://visathing.com/visa-consultancy-support/\"><strong>&nbsp;Visa Consultancy</strong></a></h5>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As there is no Embassy or Consulate of&nbsp;<strong>Cote d&rsquo;Ivoire&nbsp;</strong>in Dhaka, Bangladesh. One have to go through the nearest Embassy which is in India.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Embassy of Cote d&rsquo;Ivoire</strong><br />\r\n63 Poorvi Marg, Vasant Vihar<br />\r\nNew Delhi-110057, India.<br />\r\nPhone: (+91) 11 4604 3000<br />\r\nEmail:&nbsp;<u>embassy@amb2ci-inde.org</u></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But if you have all the below documents,&nbsp;<strong>VISAThing will provide you the Processing / Logistics support to have your visa stamped&nbsp;from Bangladesh</strong>&nbsp;(Logistics charge applicable).&nbsp;<strong>You do not need to visit the embassy in New Delhi, India to process your visa.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h6><em>VISAThing&nbsp;Facilitates you with Cote d&rsquo;Ivoire visa from Bangladesh.</em></h6>\r\n\r\n<h4>&nbsp;Fees &amp; Processing Time</h4>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>VISA PROCESSING FEE</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"width:915px\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;Number of Entry</td>\r\n			<td>Application Center Fee (BDT)</td>\r\n			<td>Logistics charge (BDT)</td>\r\n			<td>Total (BDT)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Single</strong></td>\r\n			<td>10,500/-</td>\r\n			<td>25000/-</td>\r\n			<td><strong>35,500/-</strong></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;Multiple</td>\r\n			<td>10,500/-</td>\r\n			<td>25000/-</td>\r\n			<td><strong>35,500/-</strong></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>** 15% VAT is applicable on VISAThing&rsquo;s service (logistic) charge.</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PROCESSING TIME</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Total approximate time is&nbsp;10 to&nbsp;12 working days (3 to&nbsp;5 working days at Embassy&nbsp;<strong>+&nbsp;</strong>7 working days for Passport transit).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>&nbsp;Consultancy</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Premium Visa Consultancy for Over 86 Countries in the World is a 360 degree approach. It enables you to prepare your visa application perfectly according to your profile. Proper visa documentation depends on several factors. Hence, we conduct a complete background and travel history check on the client. Based on that, accurate customized consultation is provided. Clients are carefully explained the specific documents&rsquo; requirements for visa application to improve its acceptability. Under this hood, we do all the pre-application document screening on your behalf. We provide visa support for over 70 countries which doesn&rsquo;t have Embassy presence in Bangladesh, to free you from any recurring hassles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We will open up a case file under your name and details to analyze your travel and professional history. Then, we will prepare the best possible approach for a successful visa application. You can only avail our Visa Consultancy Support upon purchase of the service and once you have agreed to our terms &amp; conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please call our hotline numbers to book your consultancy slot.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Our con