ref=\"https://www.visathing.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Cote-d---Ivorie.pdf\"><strong>Please Click Here</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>b . Two (2) passport size photographs with visiting card.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>c . Photocopies of the first three (03) pages of the passport</p>\r\n\r\n<p>d . Valid yellow fever certificat</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px\">for more information :&nbsp;https://visathing.com/country/cote-divoire/</span></p>\r\n', '2018-09-11', '2021-02-20', 1),
