(149, 'Montserrat', 'MSR', 'ms.png', '<h2>Bangladesh Visa Requirements</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>When you apply for a Bangladesh visa, you need to have several documents which support the purpose of your visit, such as:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The printed Bangladesh Visa application form</li>\r\n	<li>Your passport, which is valid for at least six more months</li>\r\n	<li>Passport-size pictures taken in front of a white background</li>\r\n	<li>Proof of payment of the Bangladesh visa fee (check the payment requirements of the Bangladesh diplomatic mission where you&rsquo;re applying)</li>\r\n	<li><strong>For Bangladesh Tourist Visa:</strong>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Flight itinerary</li>\r\n		<li>Hotel reservation or a letter of invitation from a host along with their passport</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><strong>For Bangladesh Business Visa:</strong>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Letter from your employer</li>\r\n		<li>Letter of Invitation from the company hosting you in Bangladesh</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><strong>For Bangladesh Investor Visa:</strong>&nbsp;A Letter of Recommendation from BOI/BEPZA</li>\r\n	<li><strong>For Bangladesh Researcher Visa:</strong>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>A Letter of Recommendation from the relevant Bangladesh Ministry</li>\r\n		<li>A letter from your institution in your home country</li>\r\n		<li>Letter of invitation from the institution in Bangladesh</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><strong>For Bangladesh Governmental/Diplomatic Visa:&nbsp;</strong>A Note Verbale</li>\r\n	<li><strong>For Bangladesh Journalist Visa:</strong>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>FF-1 and FF-2 application forms, completed</li>\r\n		<li>List of the equipment you will take to Bangladesh with you</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><strong>For Bangladesh Student Visa:</strong>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Letter of enrollment in your university</li>\r\n		<li>Proof of financial solvency (bank statements)</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><strong>For Bangladesh Employment Visa:</strong>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Letter from your employer in Bangladesh</li>\r\n		<li>A Letter of Recommendation from BEPZA/BOI</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><strong>For Bangladesh Family Visa:&nbsp;</strong>Proof of family relations</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>for more information :&nbsp;</strong><strong>https://visaguide.world/asia/bangladesh-visa/</strong></span></p>\r\n', '2018-09-11', '2021-02-20', 1),
