(171, 'Panama', 'PAN', 'pa.png', '<h4>&nbsp;Basic information</h4>\r\n\r\n<h5><a href=\"https://www.visathing.com/ground-support/\"><strong>&nbsp;Ground support</strong></a><br />\r\n<strong>&nbsp;Visa Consultancy</strong></h5>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bangladeshi Citizens are required to have the stamped visa, this kind is only available through a Panamanian consulate or embassy.&nbsp;As there is no consulate and embassy in Dhaka, nearest Panamanian Embassy is in India.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Embassy of Panama</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://visathingexpress.com/\">Click here</a>&nbsp;to know any kind of information about Panama visa process</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>&nbsp;Ground Support</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Now visa application lodgment in India is easier &amp; hassle free with&nbsp;<strong>VISAThing&rsquo;s Ground Support</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Why Do You Need</strong>&nbsp;<strong>VISAThing&rsquo;s Ground Support</strong>?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Some countries having embassies located in India requires the personal presence of the visa applicant at the Embassy/VFS for in-person interview or biometric data collection. The applicant must visit the embassy in India to submit the visa application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Most of the applicants face difficulty in</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>preparing an error visa application with all the necessary documents</li>\r\n	<li>the submission procedures at the embassy</li>\r\n	<li>navigating through the city and finding suitable lodging&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.visathing.com/ground-support/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">&hellip;Read more</a></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;Check List</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>1 . Two visa application form&nbsp;to be duly filled; to be filled in original without any scratches/white liquid etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2 . Three recent passport size photos&nbsp;taken in a clear white background face uncovered.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3 . Photocopy of all pages of the&nbsp;valid passport&nbsp;with&nbsp;<u>minimum