(193, 'Samoa', 'WSM', 'ws.png', '<h4>&nbsp;Basic information</h4>\r\n\r\n<h5>For Samoa, VISAThing provides</h5>\r\n\r\n<h5>&nbsp;</h5>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nationals of Bangladesh can obtain an Entry (or Transit) Permit for a max. stay of 60 days on arrival.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;Check List</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Entry Requirements</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are a number of key requirements that each traveler to Samoa must meet before they will be granted entry to the country. Each visitor to Samoa must:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. have a return or onward ticket;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. possess a passport valid for a minimum of six (6) months after the intended date of departure from Samoa;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. have a valid visa or permit for entry into the country to which they will travel from Samoa;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. state their accommodation arrangements, be they holiday accommodation such as a hotel or resort or with family or friends (specifically the village and family name);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. have documented evidence of sufficient funds for self-support (typically a copy of a bank statement);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. have no record or deportation from other countries;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7. have no health problems that would pose a risk to Samoa;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8. have no history of criminal charges resulting in a minimum of one year of sentencing; and</p>\r\n\r\n<p>9. Not be on any alert or warning lists.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:22px\">for all information :&nbsp;https://visathing.com/country/samoa/</span></p>\r\n', '2018-09-11', '2021-02-24', 1),
(194, 'San Marino', 'SMR', 'sm.png', '<p>1.&nbsp;<strong>Passport:</strong>&nbsp;Original Passport with validity of a minimum of six months after the intended date of departure and a minimum of two blank pages for visa stamp.<br />\r\n&ndash; Copy of previous passports and visas issued<br />\r\n&ndash; Attach all your old passports</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2.&nbsp;<strong>Visa Application Form:</strong>&nbsp;Visa application form will be filled with required information using block letters and black ink only.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3.<strong>&nbsp;Photo:</strong>&nbsp;Three recent passport size photographs,<br />\r\n&ndash; With matt or semi-matt finish,<br />\r\n&ndash; Photographs should be white background, without border,<br />\r\n&ndash; 60-80% face coverage, (Size: 3.5cm X 4.5cm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4.&nbsp;<strong>Work permit/Invitation for employment:</strong>&nbsp;Invitation Letter from Serbia inviting Company giving his contact details<br />\r\non its letterhead with authorized stamp and signature.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5.&nbsp;<strong>Employment Contract:</strong>&nbsp;A valid, signed, and stamped contract agreement between the applicant and the employer with available details of all the terms of employment, validity, all the relevant benefits such as medical insurance, accommodation, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6.&nbsp;<strong>Airline:</strong>&nbsp;One-way ticket itinerary as per travel date.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h4>&nbsp;Fees &amp; Processing Time</h4>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>VISA PROCESSING FEE</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Visa Type</td>\r\n			<td>Visa Fee (BDT)</td>\r\n			<td>Logistics charge (BDT)</td>\r\n			<td>Total (BDT)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Short Term</td>\r\n			<td>7950/-</td>\r\n			<td>25,000/-</td>\r\n			<td>32950/-</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Long Term</td>\r\n			<td>4350/-</td>\r\n			<td>25,000/-</td>\r\n			<td>29350/-</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Processing Time:</strong>&nbsp;Total approximate time is 2 to 4 weeks (1-3 weeks at Embassy&nbsp;<strong>+&nbsp;</strong>7 working days for Passport transit).</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>&nbsp;Consultancy</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Premium Visa Consultancy for Over 86 Countries in the World is a 360 degree approach. It enables you to prepare your visa application perfectly according to your profile. Proper visa documentation depends on several factors. Hence, we conduct a complete background and travel history check on the client. Based on that, accurate customized consultation is provided. Clients are carefully explained the specific documents&rsquo; requirements for visa application to improve its acceptability. Under this hood, we do all the pre-application document screening on your behalf. We provide visa support for over 70 countries which doesn&rsquo;t have Embassy presence in Bangladesh, to free you from any recurring hassles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We will open up a case file under your name and details to analyze your travel and professional history. Then, we will prepare the best possible approach for a successful visa application. You can only avail our Visa Consultancy Support upon purchase of the service and once you have agreed to our terms &amp; conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please call our hotline numbers to book your consultancy slot.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Our consultancy services include:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 . Studying Your Background &amp; Travel History,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2 . Creating Checklist based on Profile Merit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3 . Identifying Loop Holes and Eliminating those,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4 . Preparing Best Visa Application Approach.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tele-Consultancy Services for Distant Clients:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you&rsquo;re not able to reach us in person, you can still take our Consultancy support. We can arrange Audio/Video Consultancy at your preferred time over Skype/What&rsquo;sApp or any convenient application. Please email us for details &amp; call for appointment (Sunday to Thursday).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px\">for more information :&nbsp;https://visathing.com/check/</span></p>\r\n', '2018-09-11', '2021-02-24', 1),
