(227, 'Trinidad and Tobago', 'TTO', 'tt.png', '<h4>&nbsp;</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>High Commission of the</strong>&nbsp;<strong>Republic of Trinidad and Tobago</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But, If you have all the below documents,&nbsp;<strong>VISA Thing</strong>&nbsp;<strong>will provide you the Processing / Logistics support to have your visa stamped from Bangladesh</strong>&nbsp;(Logistics charge applicable).&nbsp;<strong>You do not need to visit the embassy in New Delhi, India to process your visa.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h4>&nbsp;Consultancy</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>VISAThing provides&nbsp;<strong>personalized visa consultancy service</strong>&nbsp;for Trinidad &amp; Tobago (Consultancy fee applicable).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Premium Visa Consultancy for Over 86 Countries in the World is a 360-degree approach. It enables you to prepare your visa application perfectly according to your profile. Proper visa documentation depends on several factors.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.visathing.com/visa-consultancy/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">&hellip;Read more</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4>&nbsp;Ground Support</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Now visa application lodgment in India is easier &amp; hassle free with&nbsp;<strong>VISAThing&rsquo;s Ground Support</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Why Do You Need</strong>&nbsp;<strong>VISAThing&rsquo;s Ground Support</strong>?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Some countries having embassies located in India requires personal presence of the visa applicant at the Embassy/VFS for in person interview or biometric data collection. The applicant must visit the embassy in India to submit the visa application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Most of the applicants face difficulty in</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Preparing an error visa application with all the necessary documents</li>\r\n	<li>The submission procedures at the embassy</li>\r\n	<li>Navigating through the city and finding suitable lodging&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.visathing.com/ground-support/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">&hellip;Read more</a></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;Check List</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>VISA REQUIREMENTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Visa Application forms (2 sets). To Download,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.visathing.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Trinidad_Tobago1.pdf\">Please Click here</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Two (2) photographs &amp; visiting cards (if any)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Original passport</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Invitation Letter from the person residing or organization having an office in Trinidad and Tobago</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. Travel Itinerary with necessary details</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. Bank Statement (From the Person/Organization who is bearing the travel cost)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7. Hotel accommodation (if any)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8. A Cover letter (self-written) and/or A Forwarding letter / NOC from the&nbsp;relevant organization (if any)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kindly note:</strong>&nbsp;If the consular section is not satisfied with the above documents, may ask for&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">for more informatin :&nbsp;https://visathing.com/country/trinidad-tobago/</span></p>\r\n', '2018-09-11', '2021-02-25', 1);
