/h5>\r\n\r\n<p>Invitation Letter from Tunisia host / Inviting Company on its letterhead stating the purpose of visit and duration of travel, duly attested by Municipal Corporation in Tunisia. The letter should be faxed directly to the embassy and a copy to us.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommendation Letter through recognized Chamber of Commerce in Bangladesh.</p>\r\n\r\n<h5><strong>7. Financial:</strong></h5>\r\n\r\n<p>Bank statement for the last six months with bank seal and stamp.</p>\r\n\r\n<h5><strong>8. Ticket:</strong></h5>\r\n\r\n<p>Confirmed Round-trip Air Ticket.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Please Note:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>a. Copy of certified identity document with applicant&rsquo;s photo. (ID card or Driver license)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>b. The application should be submitted before ten days of departure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>c. One set copy of all documents is required.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px\">for more information :&nbsp;https://visathing.com/country/tunisia/</span></p>\r\n', '2018-09-11', '2021-02-25', 1),
